P(x)= \left\{   \begin{array}{lr}     a_1 & : l_1\leq x < l_2,\\     a_2 & : l_2\leq x < l_3,\\ {}\,\vdots\\     a_n & : l_{n}\leq x < l_{n+1},\\   \end{array} \right. 
\sum_{i=1}^n a_i(l_{i+1}-l_i)=1
F(x)=a_{n(x)}(x-l_{n(x)})+\sum_{i=1}^{n(x)-1} a_i(l_{i+1}-l_i),
\displaystyle n(x)=\max_{i,x>l_i}\  i
